        <br><br>
        <h2>Translation caching </h2>
        <br>
        <p>
            You need to pass 3 key value pairs in x-www-form-urlencoded in postman and post them<br>
            text : text to be translated <br>
            sourceLanguage : language of your text <br>
            targetLanguage : language in which you want to translate text <br>  
        </p>
        <br><br>
        <h4>
            <u>API Call</u>
        </h4>
        <p>To call api u need to put <b>{url}/translate</b> and pass the above values</p>
        
